Class ManualFeedConsumptionEndPoint

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.outbrain.aletheia.PrettyToStringEndPoint

        • com.outbrain.aletheia.datum.consumption.ManualFeedConsumptionEndPoint
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    EndPoint, Serializable

    public class ManualFeedConsumptionEndPoint
extends ConsumptionEndPoint
    A ConsumptionEndPoint which holds incoming data in-memory, and can be used a synchronized produced-consumer flow. A ManualFeedConsumptionEndPoint will block the producing side once it's over the limits, and similarly will block consumption when there is nothing to consume.
